---
title: Moroccan Lentil & Cauliflower Pie with Parmesan Mash & Herbed Yoghurt
description: No-one will want to miss dinner when this irresistible veggie pie is on the menu! With a saucy chermoula-spiced lentil filling, creamy Parmesan-laced mash and yoghurt infused with garlic and parsley, it’s humble home cooking at its finest.
